ch.codebulb.lambdaomega.abstractions

Interface IndexedIFunctions<K,V>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FunctionsI, I<K,V>, IndexedI<K,V>, ReadonlyIndexedI<K,V>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IndexedIFunctionsS<K,V>, IndexedIS<K,V>, IndexedListI<K,V>, IndexedListIS<K,V>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    L, M, V2.LV2

    public interface IndexedIFunctions<K,V>
extends IndexedI<K,V>, FunctionsI
    Adds a contract to work with functional interfaces to a IndexedI. None of these functions alter the original wrapped collection.
